[{"question":"I don\u0027t think you two have ever been together for a primetime interview, have you?","answer":"No, actually, we haven\u0027t.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":15,"aSentId":16},{"question":"How long have you been together?","answer":"Eight years.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":34,"aSentId":35},{"question":"Do you know -- do you feel like you\u0027re having the last laugh for all those who mocked it?","answer":"Well, I feel like anyone who is sort of engaging themselves in tabloid press as fact will -- you know you\u0027ll always have the last laugh.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":37,"aSentId":38},{"question":"How do you make it work?","answer":"Well, one, I think you have to make your relationship a priority.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":59,"aSentId":60},{"question":"Is he -- is he romantic?","answer":"I would say so.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":82,"aSentId":83},{"question":"Or is he ruggedly you know?","answer":"No, he\u0027s very --","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":84,"aSentId":85},{"question":"Tucked you over his shoulder and wheel you home for dinner?","answer":"I think he\u0027s a little bit -- I think he\u0027s a little bit of both.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":86,"aSentId":87},{"question":"Really?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":90,"aSentId":91},{"question":"What\u0027s your favorite Post-It note?","answer":"Wow, my favorite.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":95,"aSentId":96},{"question":"You are a little old softie, aren\u0027t you?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":98,"aSentId":99},{"question":"Are you happy with how he\u0027s gone on?","answer":"Yes, I am.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":110,"aSentId":111},{"question":"When you first got into this, did you ever imagine it would become a primary new source in that way?","answer":"No.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":140,"aSentId":141},{"question":"What are the rules?","answer":"The rules -- the phone goes down at dinner.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":169,"aSentId":170},{"question":"But isn\u0027t it slightly perverse?","answer":"It is slightly perverse.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":190,"aSentId":191},{"question":"How big of a factor was it that you\u0027ve got three young girls yourself and you could look at them and perhaps see them transplanted into this hideous world?","answer":"Well, the average age of entry into the sex trade is 13 years old, and that\u0027s globally.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":215,"aSentId":216},{"question":"Why was that, do you think?","answer":"Well, I think that there\u0027s -- I think that there\u0027s a subsect of what we\u0027re looking at it and it\u0027s sort of dangerously bleeds over into something that people are very accustomed to.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":228,"aSentId":229},{"question":"Prostitution?","answer":"Right.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":231,"aSentId":232},{"question":"What do you think about that conundrum?","answer":"That\u0027s why we\u0027re using social media for this campaign, is to actually go right into the heart of where it\u0027s taking place.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":272,"aSentId":273},{"question":"And so was he deceitful in the kind of person that he described himself as?","answer":"He lied to me about his age.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":304,"aSentId":305},{"question":"I mean is this a familiar story of how these things start?","answer":"No, what she\u0027s describing is -- I mean the stories do start to take on a very similar kind of framework with the pimp.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":314,"aSentId":315},{"question":"And what did he put you through?","answer":"Well, at first he told me, you know, I\u0027ll take you shopping and I will give you anything that you want and I\u0027ll take you out of the life that you\u0027re in.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":318,"aSentId":319},{"question":"What was going on?","answer":"At first it was just him, and then when I had escaped to get home, I had to call somebody.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":333,"aSentId":334},{"question":"And how old were you then?","answer":"I was around 14, 15.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":337,"aSentId":338},{"question":"Finally, what would you say to other girls who find themselves in the same kind of situation?","answer":"I would tell them to go to an adult that is trustworthy, and that would listen to them, and that they\u0027re worthwhile waiting on, and they have a lot of people that do care about them, and that is there for them.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":362,"aSentId":363},{"question":"You know, this a multi-faceted form of abuse, isn\u0027t it?","answer":"And then the abuse continues.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":379,"aSentId":380},{"question":"How do those girls without the help of organizations like yourselves ever get out of that cycle?","answer":"Yeah.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":433,"aSentId":434},{"question":"How much money is the U.S. government spending on, say, policing drugs compared to sex slavery?","answer":"Great question, Piers.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":473,"aSentId":474},{"question":"If you were in charge of policy in this area, what is the key thing that should be done?","answer":"Well, first, look, the reason why we\u0027ve initiated this campaign is we have to create awareness.","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":479,"aSentId":480},{"question":"I mean, could you be in this for 30 years?","answer":"Probably longer,","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":529,"aSentId":530},{"question":"What are you up to now movie-wise?","answer":"I just finished a movie called \"New Year\u0027s Eve.\"","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":553,"aSentId":554},{"question":"Has that taken over in priorities for both of you?","answer":"Yes, I --","docId":"110414pmt","qSentId":563,"aSentId":564}]